# Product Ops Sandbox

This repo turns scattered product signals into product decisions for a fictional product. See
`AGENTS.md` for the full workflow map.

To run a workflow:

1. Read the matching prompt in `ai-workflows/prompts/` (classify_feedback, synthesize_research,
   detect_opportunities, or weekly_product_insights).
2. Read the notes in `input-notes/`.
3. Write the result to `outputs/`: a `.json` draft that matches the schema in
   `ai-workflows/schemas/`, plus a readable `.md` summary. (The weekly readout is Markdown only.)

Use only the evidence in the notes. Do not invent facts, numbers, or company names. Keep all data
fictional, anonymized, or approved. AI drafts; humans review; teams decide.
